&lt;p&gt;All bots, obviously.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:1" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:2"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dang, my computer is kind of a jerk.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:2" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:3"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All of the pay-to-play drivers (Siegel, Simpson, Robb) have fallen significantly since the start of the season. This could be due to talent really shining through this season, or it could be that the model doesn&amp;rsquo;t quite adequately capture driver effects vs team effects and so less-talented drivers will sift to the bottom as more &amp;ldquo;real&amp;rdquo; data comes in, or it could just be a coincidence - which would help explain why Dixon of all people is sandwiched between these three at the bottom.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:3" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:4"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I don&amp;rsquo;t know how it&amp;rsquo;s possible to overperform already sky-high expectations while also DNFing one of four races. In video game terms, I think Palou is over trying to beat the game and has moved on to trying to unlock every achievement. Someone needs to tell him the real world isn&amp;rsquo;t supposed to work that way&amp;hellip;&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:4" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:5"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Complimentary, obviously.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:5" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:6"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assuming you are one of my three human readers and not my thousands of bot followers.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:6" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:7"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alex would clean the floor with Max too probably. There really is no hope.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:7" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
